15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 6-186.1 of Title 70, unless
18 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. The Commission for Educational Quality and Accountability
20 shall establish and maintain a two-year pilot program to be known as
21 TeachForwardOK to provide new, high-quality pathways to enter the
22 teaching profession and increase the number of teachers in this
23 state’s workforce.
24
